pageProduct.name: Swisse Beauty Sleep & Renew Booster 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Beauty Sleep and Renew Booster is a unique beauty nutrition formula, with targeted skin nutrients to support skin regeneration and repair. Also rich in chamomile and hops to support healthy restful beauty sleep.

High dose vitamin A supports skin health and general wellbeing.

Vitamin C helps support collagen formation, skin regeneration and skin firmness.

Vitamin A, C and E help reduce free radical damage to body cells.

Chamomile and hops, traditionally used in Western herbal medicine, to support restful beauty sleep and help calm the nervous system.

High strength vitamin A.

Rich in chamomile and hops.

Size: 30 Capsules

Warnings

The recommended daily amount of vitamin A from all sources is 700 micrograms RE for women and 900 micrograms RE for men. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

EACH SOFT CAPSULE CONTAINS: Vitamin A (retinol palmitate) 397.8 micrograms; Vitamin C (ascorbic acid) 100 mg; Vitamin E (d-alpha-tocopheryl acid succinate) 14.5 mg; Hops (Humulus lupulus extract 62.5 mg) equiv. dry fruit 500 mg; Chamomile (Matricaria chamomilla extract 300 mg) equiv. dry flower 6 g.

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:
WARNING: If you are pregnant or considering becoming pregnant do not take vitamin A supplements without consulting your doctor or pharmacist. When taken in excess of 3000 micrograms RE vitamin A can cause birth defects.
One soft capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Adult Dosage: WARNING: If you are pregnant or considering becoming pregnant do not take vitamin A supplements without consulting your doctor or pharmacist. When taken in excess of 3000 micrograms RE vitamin A can cause birth defects.
One soft capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place.
